  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers\", \"name\": \"RunGuardsAndResolvers\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/router/src/models.ts#L242-L267\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"runguardsandresolvers\">RunGuardsAndResolvers<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#runguardsandresolvers\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label type-alias\">type-alias</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A policy for when to run guards and resolvers on a route.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers\" class=\"code-anchor\">RunGuardsAndResolvers</a> = 'pathParamsChange' | 'pathParamsOrQueryParamsChange' | 'paramsChange' | 'paramsOrQueryParamsChange' | 'always' | ((from: <a href=\"api/router/ActivatedRouteSnapshot\" class=\"code-anchor\">ActivatedRouteSnapshot</a>, to: <a href=\"api/router/ActivatedRouteSnapshot\" class=\"code-anchor\">ActivatedRouteSnapshot</a>) => boolean);\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/router/Route#runGuardsAndResolvers\"><code>Route#runGuardsAndResolvers</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Guards and/or resolvers will always run when a route is activated or deactivated. When a route is\nunchanged, the default behavior is the same as <code>paramsChange</code>.</p>\n<p><code>paramsChange</code> : Rerun the guards and resolvers when path or\npath param changes. This does not include query parameters. This option is the default.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>always</code> : Run on every execution.</li>\n<li><code>pathParamsChange</code> : Rerun guards and resolvers when the path params\nchange. This does not compare matrix or query parameters.</li>\n<li><code>paramsOrQueryParamsChange</code> : Run when path, matrix, or query parameters change.</li>\n<li><code>pathParamsOrQueryParamsChange</code> : Rerun guards and resolvers when the path params\nchange or query params have changed. This does not include matrix parameters.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router\n - api/router/OnSameUrlNavigation\n - api/router/Route\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/router\n - api/router/ActivatedRouteSnapshot\n - api/router/Route#runGuardsAndResolvers\n - api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#description\n - api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#runguardsandresolvers\n - api/router/RunGuardsAndResolvers#see-also\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/router/src/models.ts#L242-L267\n-->"
}